ng optimisation on Linux.</li>\n<li>Regex 1.1.0 brings in some performance improvements for (git)ignore patterns</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Some progress towards manual restarts</h2>\n<p>As part of the API changes, file-triggered runs and manual runs are now explicitly differentiated, which will help when eventually implementing <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"260532309\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/67\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/watchexec/watchexec/issues/67/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/issues/67\">#67</a>.</p>","downloads":[{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/1.10.0/watchexec-1.10.0-i686-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz","filename":"watchexec-1.10.0-i686-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz","size":1260008,"format":{"short":"GZ","long":"Gzipped tarball","tool":"tar xzf"},"sums":[],"cats":["Linux","x86","musl"]},{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/1.10.0/watchexec-1.10.0-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb","filename":"watchexec-1.10.0-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.deb","size":887818,"format":{"short":"DEB","long":"Debian/Ubuntu package","tool":"dpkg -i"},"sums":[],"cats":["Linux","x86-64","glibc"]},{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/1.10.0/watchexec-1.10.0-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.gz","filename":"watchexec-1.10.0-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu.tar.gz","size":1186664,"format":{"short":"GZ","long":"Gzipped tarball","tool":"tar xzf"},"sums":[],"cats":["Linux","x86-64","glibc"]},{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/download/1.10.0/watchexec-1.10.0-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz","filename":"watchexec-1.10.0-x86_64-unknown-linux-musl.tar.gz","size":1290075,"format":{"short":"GZ","long":"Gzipped tarball","tool":"tar xzf"},"sums":[],"cats":["Linux","x86-64","musl"]},{"url":"https://github.com/watchexec/watchexec/releases/down